@olympiansmp In regards to lore and role play, I actively DM for 2 dnd campaigns and play in 3! I’m practiced in characterization, writing 3-dimensional characters with space for growth, and working with other ppl as a team in both the onscreen and behind the scenes aspects of storytelling ⬇️

@olympiansmp I adore PJO and related series! As a child I was heavily invested in Greek mythology (an incredibly watered down version of it as I was, in fact, a child) and it has never quite left my list of things I will drop everything else to invest in. ⬇️
